{"tid":861824,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"脱髮可以點自救，有咩好產品推介？","createTime":"2018-10-14T12:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T02:35:56.000Z","uid":102561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7467245588c7ba06d5fd392669f59f92d848ca82","tid":861824,"uid":102561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"之前八月尾剪頭髮比個髮型師話我頭髮稀疏<br />\n我已經有d膽心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但果陣冇乜理 剪完頭髮冇耐應該唔覺眼<br />\n但最近見到自己個頭仲薄薄地<br />\n屋企人都話我個頭光光地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前一兩年自己d頭髮仲夠硬正<br />\n而家髮質就明顯軟左<br />\n但係屋企人就唔係幾理我，冇帶我睇專科<br />\n自己就廿頭學生哥冇乜錢，想睇下有d咩方法可以救返d頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想d頭髮質硬返少少同生返d頭髮<br />\n仲有小弟發現自己呢一年內兩邊鼻翼成日出鼻油<br />\n唔知關唔關甩頭髮事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f63deca30b47ee09ee2c11fe327f62188fdb09","tid":861824,"uid":102561,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"唔知自己情況算唔算嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係地中海定雄秃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/201635_ce88013e024148bc0ebbe06bc87b51a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F201635_ce88013e024148bc0ebbe06bc87b51a4.jpg&h=ea121e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/201637_2f8cf2f9efd74228c491cd36d9cdb979.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F201637_2f8cf2f9efd74228c491cd36d9cdb979.jpg&h=8bb2220f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/201639_1f0cc3b8f24b140e410e9941a1a15b45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20